body:
Okay, when I do that, there is quite a lot printed, but neither output has anything from either of those files. I'm running:
`TF_XLA_FLAGS=--xla_generate_hlo_graph=.* python mnist.py &> out_xla`
and
`python mnist.py --xla='' &> out_xla`
and searching for 'xla_device_launch_op' and 'xla_local_launch_op' in the file out_xla each time, and neither is found.
